data.description: Assumable mortgage. Welcome to the Hayden, an exceptional gem among DR Horton’s exquisite floor plans with Immediate Move-In. As you step into this haven, you’re immediately greeted by its robust concrete block construction spanning both floors, ensuring stability, durability, and peace of mind for you and your loved ones.    The versatile flex space on the main level caters to your modern lifestyle needs – whether that’s a cozy home office to fulfill your work-from-home duties or a formal dining room for those special occasions. Additionally, the main level boasts a spacious bedroom accompanied by a full bath, a warm central living room to gather around, and an inviting open kitchen. And the cherry on top? An extended island perfect for morning breakfasts, evening wine chats, or anything in between.    But there's more! Ascend to the second level and find yourself in the midst of a generous owner's suite, designed for ultimate relaxation and rejuvenation. The secondary living room upstairs sets the stage for countless family movie nights and cherished memories. Plus, the handy second-floor laundry room brings convenience right to your fingertips.    Situated in North Park Isle, Plant City, you're not just buying a home; you're investing in a lifestyle. Nestled right off Sam Allen Rd and North Park Rd, with easy access to I-4, the historic downtown weaves a tapestry of charm with monthly markets, quaint shops, and delectable dining experiences along Main Street. Not to mention, you're in proximity to the world-renowned Strawberry Festival.    Yearning for a metropolitan experience? Being strategically located between Lakeland, Orlando, and Tampa, you're spoilt for choice with an array of entertainment opportunities. Yet, the beauty of North Park Isle is that it still retains its serene, rural ambiance.    As a resident, immerse yourself in resort-style amenities: Challenge friends to a game of pickleball or basketball, or take a leisurely swim in the pool, crowned by a breezy cabana. For the nature enthusiasts, the community offers picturesque pond and conservation views, as well as a kayak launch into one of its expansive lakes.    This residence is powered by D.R. Horton’s state-of-the-art Smart Home System. Experience the Hayden in North Park Isle - where luxury meets tranquility. Make it yours today!
